ğŸ”§ Feature Engineering: Create rolling window sequences and compute RUL targets.

ğŸ¤– Model Training: Train LSTM/GRU models to predict RUL.

ğŸ“Š Model Evaluation: Evaluate performance using RMSE and visualize predictions.

âš ï¸ Risk Thresholding: Set thresholds to trigger maintenance alerts.

ğŸ“ˆ Visualization & Output: Present trends and predictions via charts and dashboards.

